TITLE: Episode 29 - Boot Breath
DESCRIPTION: This week, Ryan Burgett of Techo-Agorist joins me again. We talk about China's document leak about their repression of Muslims, the UPS murders, Amazon's Doorbell spy cameras, Deep State torture, the FBI's self-snitching program, and a Trump impeachment update. We also examine Operation Northwoods in the Red Pill of the Week.
